\c 75 Rwiyo rwokuvonga Mwari Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbi‑ rwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raAsafi. Rwiyo. 1 Tinokuvongai, Mwari; Tinovonga, nokuti zita renyu riri pedyo; Vanhu vanoparidza mabasa enyu anoshamisa. 2 "Kana ndichiwana nguva yakafanira, Ndichatonga zvakarurama. 3 Pasi pose panyauka navose vagerepo; Ndini ndakamisa mbiru dzayo. 4 Ndakati. huka Nax‘a. max‘yami, `Regai kuita namanyawi;' Nokuna vakaipa, `Regai kusimudza runyanga.' 5 Regai kusimudza runyanga rwenyu kudenga;
